-- Madagascar Owes Building Companies $47.6 Million, l’Express Says
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2012-04-16T06:05:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-16/madagascar-owes-building-companies-47-6-million-l-express-says.html
Madagascar’s arrears to the
country’s building companies amounts to 100 billion ariary ($48
million), Antananarivo-based l’Express de Madagascar reported on
its  website , without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
